</div>";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 25 Jun 2008 16:23:00 +0000";s:4:"guid";s:83:"http://www.37signals.com/svn/posts/1107-mike-rohdes-amazing-sketchnotes-from-seed-3";s:4:"link";s:83:"http://www.37signals.com/svn/posts/1107-mike-rohdes-amazing-sketchnotes-from-seed-3";s:7:"summary";s:4230:"<p><a href="http://www.rohdesign.com/weblog/">Mike Rohde</a> did another great job <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/rohdesign/sets/72157605489759516/">drawing sketchnotes at the <span class="caps">SEED 3</span> Conference on June 6th, 2008</a> (below). <a href="http://www.seedconference.com/list.php">Sign up to get notified</a> when we announce the next <span class="caps">SEED</span>.</p>


	<p><img src="http://www.37signals.com/svn/images/2559574197_b9a01bf721.jpg" width="500" height="395" alt="SEED 3" /></p>


	<p><img src="http://www.37signals.com/svn/images/2559575595_197a1402d8.jpg" width="500" height="395" alt="SEED 3" /></p>


